# bits 31-28 of the Device Identification Register
# Revision A (BSR length 735) seems to be more common than revision 0 (BSR length 738).
# Unfortunately both revisions seem to have the same JTAG ID register.
# If you have problems with getting urjtag to recognise your MPC8272,
# try switching the revisions below.
#0000	mpc8272_rev0		0
0000	mpc8272_revA		0
